description: Deletes a managed endpoint. A managed endpoint is a gateway that connects Amazon EMR Studio to Amazon EMR on EKS so that Amazon EMR Studio can communicate with your virtual cluster.

parameters.name: id
parameters.description: The ID of the managed endpoint.

parameters.name: virtualClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the endpoint's virtual cluster.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The output displays the ID of the managed endpoint.

nested_items.name: virtualClusterId
nested_items.description: The output displays the ID of the endpoint's virtual cluster.
